timeline.bodyText:
I'm thinking about this from a maintenance perspective and I think it might be better if we constructed the name of the global property the same everywhere, so here and in config.xml. The way to do this would be to add a line to fhir.properties like so:
project.parent.artifactId=@project.parent.artifactId@
Then annotating this like this:
@Value("${project.parent.artifactId}.personAttributeTypeUuid")
public static String PERSON_ATTRIBUTE_TYPE_PROPERTY;
Does this seem like a good idea to you?

